name: Experiment Or Die #108
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. I have always been good with numbers and science despite my creative leanings, and have found Physics to be the most interesting of the sciences. The nature and properties of energy and matter! This whole collection is kind of like a year long Butterfly Effect... who knows how the ideas and concepts I'm working with now will effect tomorrows piece and with each additional day the deviation from the initial path only grows. I did eventually get to a point where the math became too difficult but by then I had clearly defined my future in the arts and from then on used my TI-83 to play snake. I wonder what previous decisions led me to being so good at snake? Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
